5 means, as well as to any other assemblage of members of the ACO’s governing
6 body at which binding action is taken on behalf of the ACO. For purposes of
7 this section, the term “ACO’s governing body” shall also include the
8 governing body of any organization acting as a coordinating entity for two or
9 more ACOs that contract with Vermont Medicaid.
